k/bkn/cnt/news/20150401/bkn-20150401222030660-0401_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20150401%2Fbkn-20150401222030660-0401_00822_001.html&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2Bs2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=d7dadeac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20150401/bkn-20150401222030660-0401_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n賊爆診所以錢少求情 官指醫生是「星球人」<br />\n2015年04月01日(三) 22:20<br />\n<br />\n兩名案底累累的慣犯出獄兩個月後，竟斗膽帶備鐵筆等工具到旺角警署對面的一間診所，趁診所晚上關門後撬門圖爆竊。惟警方早已接獲線報派警員在附近埋伏，並趁他們撬開捲閘後，當場擒獲他們。他們今日(1日)在區域法院承認一項企圖爆竊罪，辯方呈上餐廳遭爆竊的案例，指本案案情不算嚴重，但法官指醫生被捧為「星球人」和「月球人」，收入每周以百萬計，若以餐廳和診所對比是「睇小咗醫生」。<br />\n<br />\n兩名被告依次是45歲陳子良，任職廚房工人，以及28歲越南裔的<span style=\"color: red;\">武玉修</span>(又名胡玉修)，任職地盤工人。首被告有78項案底，次被告則<span style=\"color: red;\">有16項案底</span>。次被告的律師求情時呈上案例，其中一宗案例的被告剛好叫「陳子良」，法官林偉權遂問該案被告是否即本案首被告，但最終找不到答案。"},{"pid":"f4db95a613da9d5dbb20aa288a9f7417db1e426d","tid":1276570,"uid":33293,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0d8e06736e33d6c55af79a1c909e121b0679f9ec","tid":1276570,"uid":77760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:46:15.000Z","msg":"有人報夢話見到依啲人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xEcrbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xEcrbc.png&h=581a52f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武玉修<br />\n有14k 新義安背景<br />\n屯門人<br />\n越南仔<br />\n冇facebook智能電話都冇 長年坐監 長期飲咳藥水同劏死牛<br />\n<br />\n又勾結外國勢力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wallace.mw.cheng/videos/10156403917891616/UzpfSTYwOTYyMzA2OToxMDE1NzE0NTc5OTgyMzA3MA/?__tn__=%2CdlC-R-R&amp;eid=ARBbOmU_SmfutKsXthJE8Tajggcnm_ve8JqldadIT75XhfyH2MhHpijtNtEnZ5vfs614L-8HTmVmoiC0&amp;hc_ref=ARQ4ZEc_dDHy3PQW6ecK4D1x62ZJD_HqblZdaBtPykl-4GeJKT6l3pk2u6zebokIS8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwallace.mw.cheng%2Fvideos%2F10156403917891616%2FUzpfSTYwOTYyMzA2OToxMDE1NzE0NTc5OTgyMzA3MA%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252CdlC-R-R%2